#. plugin:external-backup:section:5:content
#: 
msgid "Any WebDAV-compatible service works with this plugin:\n"
"\n"
"- Nextcloud (recommended)\n"
"- ownCloud\n"
"- Synology NAS\n"
"- QNAP NAS\n"
"- Box.com (with WebDAV)\n"
"- Apache mod_dav\n"
"- nginx with WebDAV module\n"
"\n"
"Note: Some services require app-specific passwords for WebDAV access."
msgstr "Svaka WebDAV-kompatibilna usluga radi s ovim dodatkom:\n"
"\n"
"- Nextcloud (preporučeno)\n"
"- ownCloud\n"
"- Synology NAS\n"
"- QNAP NAS\n"
"- Box.com (s WebDAV-om)\n"
"- Apache mod_dav\n"
"- nginx s WebDAV modulom\n"
"\n"
"Napomena: Neke usluge zahtijevaju lozinke specifične za aplikaciju za WebDAV pristup."

#. plugin:openlp:section:4:title
#: 
msgid "Authentication"
msgstr "Autentifikacija"

#. plugin:openlp:section:4:content
#: 
msgid "Authentication is required for API v2 if you've enabled it in OpenLP's Remote plugin settings. The plugin uses HTTP Basic Authentication. Most local network setups don't require authentication, but it's recommended for security."
msgstr "Autentifikacija je potrebna za API v2 ako ste je omogućili u postavkama OpenLP Udaljenog dodatka. Dodatak koristi HTTP Basic autentifikaciju. Većina postavki lokalne mreže ne zahtijeva autentifikaciju, ali se preporučuje radi sigurnosti."

#: 
msgid "Auto TLS"
msgstr "Automatski TLS"

#. plugin:external-backup:section:2:title
#: 
msgid "Auto-Backup"
msgstr "Automatska sigurnosna kopija"

#: 
msgid "BCC All Mail To"
msgstr "BCC sva pošta na"

#. plugin:external-backup:section:4:content
#: 
msgid "Before relying on external backups, test your connection:\n"
"1. Go to Plugins > External Backup\n"
"2. Click 'Test WebDAV Connection'\n"
"3. Verify you see a success message\n"
"\n"
"Common issues:\n"
"- 401/403 errors: Check username and password\n"
"- Connection timeout: Verify the endpoint URL is correct\n"
"- Certificate errors: Ensure the WebDAV server has a valid SSL certificate"
msgstr "Prije oslanjanja na vanjske sigurnosne kopije, testirajte vezu:\n"
"1. Idite na Dodaci > Vanjska sigurnosna kopija\n"
"2. Kliknite 'Testiraj WebDAV vezu'\n"
"3. Provjerite prikazuje li se poruka o uspjehu\n"
"\n"
"Uobičajeni problemi:\n"
"- 401/403 greške: Provjerite korisničko ime i lozinku\n"
"- Vremensko ograničenje veze: Provjerite je li URL krajnje točke ispravan\n"
"- Greške certifikata: Provjerite ima li WebDAV poslužitelj valjani SSL certifikat"

